@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gzlnxz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.27 / v0 + 0.80)) * wp.exp((v2 + 0.45 * v0 + 0.56)))
    v2 = tmp
    v0 = v1
    v2 = tmp
    v2 = (wp.abs(tmp) / ((v0 + 0.52 - tmp + 0.17) + (v1 + 0.97 - v2 + 0.89)))
    v1 = v2
    v0 = 0.28
    data[tid] = v0
